1. Installation & Setup

- Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Jess71902/Parking_with_biometric.git
cd smart-parking-payment-system
- Setup enviornment on VS Code
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # For Linux/Mac
venv\Scripts\activate     # For Windows
- Upgrade pip (Recommended)
python -m pip install
- Install Required Libraries
pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Project structure:
smart-parking-payment/
│
├── app.py               # Main Flask application
├── logic.py             # Face recognition & command validation logic
├── requirements.txt     # Python dependencies
├── blacklist.txt        # Malicious pattern list
│
├── templates/           # HTML templates (index.html, dashboard.html, etc.)
├── static/              # CSS, JavaScript, image assets
│   ├── style.css
│   └── script.js
└── README.md            # Project overview
